text: Fragrant Briyani rice with chicken $7. Very generous portions. Be prepared for a long queue here.

Went for dinner at 7+ and there was still a short queue. Got the plain thosai - had been left out for a while and was cold but still flavourful. Towards the sour side, which I liked. Could eat it plain if I wanted to. Dips were also room temperature but decent. Would come back again.
